com.percussion.pso.workflow
Class PSOWorkflowInfoFinder

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.pso.workflow.PSOWorkflowInfoFinder
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSOWorkflowInfoFinder
public class PSOWorkflowInfoFinder
extends Object
implements IPSOWorkflowInfoFinder

Finds basic info about the workflow state for an item. This class loads the workflow list from the system web service, and will not detect changes until the next restart.

Author:
DavidBenua
